76561198008174967,Recommended,268650,25022736,"Posted: 19 August, 2016",all,Jev,"In my opinion one of the best voxel-based game out there.Especially when you want to get a bit crazy.o You can build pretty much everything you imagine, Tanks, Hovercrafts, Planes, Spacecrafts, and all kind of buildings and so on. Land, Space, Air, Water and Underwater are the locations you can make crafts for.o The design feels very natural, every design decission you make could have benefits or consequences. Every block you place is there for a reason and changes the behavior of your craft.Say you build a ship, that can be destroyed very easily. Then you upgrade your armor, so it wont take as much damage. But higher armor increases your ship costs, weight, speed and other types of damage like emp do now more damage.Dasign is the best part of the game, and it goes deep, really deep, so deep that this the biggest turn off for casual gamers. It took me literally more than 20 hours to undestand how to build a ship, I looked alot of youtube, forums, reddit to get into the game. So this was quite an afford, and I´m still not ""there"", loaded a hovercraft from steam workshop - and literally dont understand how it works, even after 500hours of playing. And even though this sounds bad - it´s not.Thats the point, you can experiment a lot in this game, you start simple, try diffrent things, and in order to check if you understand it, I tend to build minimalistic design to capture the idea of something. Then I move on to the next chapter of block and so on.After you understand some of the game mechanics, you can design really naturally, and everything you want or imagine.You want a laser-drone-swarm ? do it. You want a super-big-laser-satellite as defense? Yeah why not. You want that thing out of the Movie you saw? ok.Weaponsystems go deep to, you can make the any type damage you like. If you want explosions, you get them. I like to make my oponnents look like cheese, shooting thru them so they have more holes then cheese could have. You can build all type of missiles you want. Actually every type of weapon is not ""modable"" but consists out of mods, thats why there are so many diffrent ways you can build and use them.I would recommend this game to everyone who likes designing crafts.Some parts of feel a bit undone and it´s not the most graphic intense game.But it´s the closest thing to this thing you imagined it can do when you played with lego."
