76561198106549122,Recommended,268650,23526591,"Posted: 12 June, 2016",all,ALIBAH'S SNAKBAH,"This is a well put together game for it being in ALPHA. I'll make this quick and easy to view:9/10 - Great replay value - Great sandbox - Price is appropriate IMOEdit: When your first vehicle functions 10/10 =)Pros:- Controls are good (keyboard based). Many are complaining about controls but I find they are well done. Keyboard based controls have a rough learning curve but after a few hours it becomes second nature.- Building is very detailed compared to other sandbox games.- This is a very challenging game. (if your into that)- The devs don't hold your hand and instead guide you in the right direction to allow you to make your own  decisions/think for yourself.- Graphics are good.. They give off a Borderlands kind of look.Cons:- Steep learning curve. Requiring you to actually research and learn the game for the first 10 hrs+ (honestly doesn't bother me.. with complexity comes difficulty and I'm ok with that.)- If you do not like to read and comprehend steps, some of the tutorial missions will ave you pulling your hair out. (although the engine repair one needs a better step system like the cannon builders ect.)- There are a few graphical issues nothing game breaking though. (very good for a Alpha)I guess I'll just come out and say it... If your a moron, short attention span or a child.. this game is not for you.. don't buy it.. you will not enjoy."
